'''Seifax''' was a front company for the [[Loronar Corporation/Legends|Loronar Corporation]] in [[13 ABY/Legends|13 ABY]] which used it to sell its products to both the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] and the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]]. Its plant on [[Antemeridias]] had been purchasing miniaturized [[Hyperdrive/Legends|hyperdrives]] from the [[Bith/Legends|Bith]].

